Package proj2

Class Summary
About This is a window for information about this program.
Create This is a module that allows someone to create a test.
CreateHelp This module shows the user how to correctly format questions when created a test by showing the user an example of each type of question.
GradeTest Allows an administrator to grade a test by loading up the answer key and a file that contains answers from a student's test.
Main Gives the user the option of creating a new test, administering a test, or grading a test.
TestStudent This module tests the student by loading up questions from a key.
